{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id783ea93f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"544n"},"text":"§ 544n.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id783ea940-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" General authorizations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"There are authorized to be appropriated for fiscal years after the fiscal year 1986 such sums as are described below; ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002435"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002435"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. The semicolon probably should be a colon."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id783ea941-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For the purpose of acquisition of lands, water and interests therein pursuant to sections 544 to 544p of this title: $40,000,000: ","children":[{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That of this amount no more than $10,000,000 shall be available to acquire lands, water, and interests therein pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544h"},"text":"section 544h of this title","children":[],"tail":". Such amounts are authorized to be appropriated from amounts covered into the Land and Water Conservation Fund notwithstanding any allocation, apportionment, or limitation contained in chapter 2003 of title 54."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id783ea942-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For the purpose of providing payments to local governments pursuant to section 544","children":[{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"(c) of this title: $2,000,000."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id783ea943-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Specific authorizations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"There are authorized to be appropriated for fiscal years after the fiscal year 1986, effective upon concurrence on the management plan pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544d"},"text":"section 544d of this title","children":[],"tail":":"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id783ea944-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For the purpose of construction of an interpretive center to be located in the State of Oregon, and a conference center to be located in the State of Washington: $10,000,000.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id783ea945-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For the purpose of construction of recreation facilities pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544e/d"},"text":"section 544e(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":": $10,000,000."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id783ea946-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For the purpose of preparing a program and restoring and reconstructing the Old Columbia River Scenic Highway, Oregon pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544j"},"text":"section 544j of this title","children":[],"tail":": $2,800,000."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id783ea947-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For the purpose of providing economic development grants pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544i"},"text":"section 544i of this title","children":[],"tail":": $5,000,000 for each State: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That funds authorized to be appropriated pursuant to this paragraph shall be available for the acquisition of lands and interests therein pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544h"},"text":"section 544h of this title","children":[],"tail":" if, at the expiration of three years, the States have failed to carry out their respective function pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544c"},"text":"section 544c of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id783ea948-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s544n/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Availability of funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Funds appropriated under subsections (a)(2) and (b) shall not be made available for any county which does not have in effect a land use ordinance which has been found to be consistent by the Commission, and concurred on by the Secretary as consistent with the management plan pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s544f"},"text":"section 544f of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id783ea949-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/663/s16"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–663, § 16","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-11-17"},"text":"Nov. 17, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/4300"},"text":"100 Stat. 4300","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/287/s5/d/17"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–287, § 5(d)(17)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3265"},"text":"128 Stat. 3265","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id783ea94a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id783ea94b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id783ea94c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/287"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–287","children":[],"tail":", which directed amendment of par. (1) by substituting “chapter 2003 of title 54” for “the Land and Water Conservation Fund ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 460","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"–4 and following)”, was executed by making the substitution for “the Land and Water Conservation Fund ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s4601–4"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 4601–4","children":[],"tail":" and following)”, to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
